# Commit convention (CI-enforced)

Source of truth: `commitlint.config.mjs`, `.commitlintrc.yml`, `docs/COMMIT_CONVENTION.md`.

## Format

```
type(scope): subject
```

- Subject max **72** characters; imperative mood (`add`, not `added`).
- Body lines max **100** characters.
- Propose commit message only — **do not** run `git commit` unless the user asks.

## Allowed types (`type-enum`)

`feat`, `fix`, `perf`, `refactor`, `test`, `bench`, `docs`, `ci`, `chore`, `build`, `revert`

## Allowed scopes (`scope-enum`)

MUST use one of these — **CI fails on unknown scopes**:

`parser`, `loader`, `pipeline`, `model`, `config`, `metrics`, `ci`, `docs`, `bench`, `benchmarks`,
`migration`, `fixtures`, `importer`, `downloader`, `oss`, `api`, `web`, `export`, `security`,
`git`, `docker`, `scripts`, `workflow`, `deps`, `repository`, `handlers`, `services`, `middleware`, `meilisearch`, `commitlint`

## Scope picker

| Scope | Use for |
|-------|---------|
| `parser`, `loader`, `pipeline`, `importer` | Import pipeline |
| `downloader` | RFB download |
| `model`, `repository`, `handlers`, `services`, `middleware` | Go packages |
| `api`, `web`, `export` | HTTP API / frontend |
| `config`, `metrics` | Config / observability |
| `migration`, `fixtures` | SQL migrations / test data |
| `docs`, `oss`, `security` | Documentation |
| `bench`, `benchmarks` | Benchmarks (`docs/benchmarks/`, TSV) |
| `ci`, `workflow`, `commitlint` | GitHub Actions, commitlint config |
| `git` | `.gitignore`, hooks, repo hygiene |
| `docker` | `docker-compose.yml`, Dockerfiles |
| `scripts` | `scripts/` shell tooling |
| `deps` | `go.mod`, `package.json` |

## Mapping examples

| Change | Scope |
|--------|-------|
| `.gitignore` | `git` |
| `docker-compose.yml` | `docker` |
| `.github/workflows/` | `workflow` or `ci` |
| `docs/benchmarks/` | `benchmarks` |
| `commitlint.config.mjs` | `ci` |

## Valid examples

- `feat(parser): add Latin-1 to UTF-8 conversion in CSV reader`
- `fix(importer): dedupe duplicate CNPJ rows during COPY`
- `docs(benchmarks): add 2026-06-24 full import report`
- `ci(commitlint): add benchmarks scope to scope-enum`
- `chore(git): ignore node_modules and scan artifacts`

## Forbidden

- Invented scopes (`repo`, `benchmark`, `workflows`) — use table above.
- Mixed-language subjects or scopes.
